<p>I am trying to replace a string value in textarea while typing in textbox with jquery. I used keypress event to try achieving that. What may be the issue here in this <a href="http://jsfiddle.net/WzE48/371/" rel="nofollow">fiddle</a>?</p>  <pre><code>&lt;input type="text" id="textbox" /&gt; &lt;textarea id="txtArea"&gt;This is a sample test.&lt;/textarea&gt; </code></pre>  <p>jquery code</p>  <pre><code>$("#textbox").keypress(function () {     var txtAreaValue = $('#txtArea').val();     var txtAreaValueAfterreplace = txtAreaValue.replace('sample', $(this).val());     $('#txtArea').val(txtAreaValueAfterreplace);  }); </code></pre>